<view class="page-shell">
  <view class="page-title">谜境补给站</view>
  <view class="page-subtitle">
    这里集中管理体力、定格符、引路符、签到、音效和自定义谜境入口，方便随时补资源再回去继续入局。
  </view>

  <view class="card">
    <view class="row-between">
      <view class="card-title">当前补给</view>
      <view class="chip">金币 {{profile.coins}}</view>
    </view>
    <view class="stats-grid">
      <view class="stats-cell">
        <view class="stats-label">体力</view>
        <view class="stats-value">{{profile.energy}} / {{profile.maxEnergy}}</view>
      </view>
      <view class="stats-cell">
        <view class="stats-label">定格符</view>
        <view class="stats-value">{{profile.unlockDragTools}}</view>
      </view>
      <view class="stats-cell">
        <view class="stats-label">引路符</view>
        <view class="stats-value">{{profile.guideHintTools}}</view>
      </view>
      <view class="stats-cell stats-cell-wide">
        <view class="stats-label">恢复倒计时</view>
        <view class="stats-value small-text">{{energyText}}</view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="card">
    <view class="row-between">
      <view class="card-title">自定义谜境</view>
      <view class="chip">相册 / 分享</view>
    </view>
    <view class="card-desc">从相册上传自己的照片生成谜境关卡，或者导入朋友发来的谜境码。</view>
    <button class="secondary-btn action-gap" bindtap="handleCustom">进入自定义中心</button>
  </view>

  <view class="card">
    <view class="row-between">
      <view class="card-title">每日签到</view>
      <view class="chip">+3 体力 +1 定格符 +1 引路符</view>
    </view>
    <view class="card-desc">每天第一次签到都会补充金币、体力、定格符和引路符，适合把当天的入局资源一次备齐。</view>
    <button class="primary-btn action-gap" bindtap="handleSignIn">立即签到</button>
  </view>

  <view class="card">
    <view class="row-between">
      <view class="card-title">补给补充</view>
      <view class="chip">{{hasRealAdUnit ? '已接真实广告' : '开发占位中'}}</view>
    </view>
    <view class="card-desc">当前已经接好激励广告封装，可以分别补体力、定格符或引路符。</view>
    <view class="grid-two action-gap">
      <button class="secondary-btn" bindtap="handleWatchAd">看广告补 2 点体力</button>
      <button class="secondary-btn" bindtap="handleWatchUnlockAd">看广告补 1 个定格符</button>
    </view>
    <button class="secondary-btn action-gap" bindtap="handleWatchGuideAd">看广告补 1 个引路符</button>
  </view>

  <view class="card">
    <view class="row-between">
      <view class="card-title">基础设置</view>
      <switch checked="{{profile.soundEnabled}}" color="#d57d49" bindchange="handleToggleSound" />
    </view>
    <view class="card-desc">后续这里还可以继续扩展成震动、背景音乐、剧情跳过和隐私授权。</view>
  </view>

  <view class="card">
    <view class="row-between">
      <view class="card-title">上线必需项</view>
      <view class="chip">隐私 / 协议 / 发布</view>
    </view>
    <view class="card-desc">提审前可以在这里查看隐私政策、用户协议和当前发布检查清单，减少漏项。</view>
    <view class="grid-two action-gap">
      <button class="secondary-btn" bindtap="handleOpenPrivacy">查看隐私政策</button>
      <button class="secondary-btn" bindtap="handleOpenAgreement">查看用户协议</button>
    </view>
    <button class="secondary-btn action-gap" bindtap="handleOpenReleaseChecklist">查看发布检查</button>
  </view>

  <view class="card">
    <view class="row-between">
      <view class="card-title">运行日志</view>
      <view class="chip">排障导出</view>
    </view>
    <view class="card-desc">已经开始记录基础埋点和错误日志。遇到问题时，你可以直接复制最近日志发给开发排查。</view>
    <view class="grid-two action-gap">
      <button class="secondary-btn" bindtap="handleCopyLogs">复制运行日志</button>
      <button class="secondary-btn" bindtap="handleClearLogs">清空运行日志</button>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
